# @tenphi/tasty-eslint-plugin — ESLint Plugin for Tasty

Package: `@tenphi/tasty-eslint-plugin` — ESLint plugin for validating `tasty()`, `tastyStatic()`, `useStyles()`, `useGlobalStyles()`, and related APIs.

## Key Features

- 27 lint rules across property, value, state, structure, and best-practice categories
- Import-aware detection (only fires on real tasty imports)
- Project config support via `tasty.config.ts`
- Recommended and strict presets
- ESLint 8+ and 9+ (flat config) support

